tely, I still got a big egg omelette with \"everything\" when they asked for what fillings I wanted. I ate that omelette in about 2 minutes. I also had an apple, donut, and a half cup of coffee. Kody gave me puppy eyes asking for food, but Mike told me not to give into them."), mdx("p", null, mdx("span", {
